This paper deals with the security and privacy of Tor onion services, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and network security (cs.NI). The paper also involves data analysis and machine learning techniques, which could be categorized under cybernetics (cs.CY) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper discusses website design and countermeasures, which could be classified under software engineering (cs.SE).
